===Chapters not yet in tankōbon format===
These chapters have yet to be published in a ''[[tankōbon]]'' volume.

==Reception==
The first collected volume of the series sold 29,288 copies, ranking number 17 on the weekly [[Oricon]] manga chart.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-01-25/japanese-comic-ranking-january-16-22/.111475 |title= Japanese Comic Ranking, January 16-22 |date= January 25, 2017 |accessdate= September 20, 2017 |publisher= [[Anime News Network]]}}</ref> Its second volume ranked number 34, selling 22,565 copies in its first week,<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-03-22/japanese-comic-ranking-march-13-19/.113769 |title= Japanese Comic Ranking, March 13-19 |date= March 22, 2017 |accessdate= September 20, 2017 |publisher= [[Anime News Network]]}}</ref> while its third debuted at number 41 with 20,445 copies sold.<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-06-28/japanese-comic-ranking-june-19-25/.118150 |title= Japanese Comic Ranking, June 19-25 |date= June 28, 2017 |accessdate= September 20, 2017 |publisher= [[Anime News Network]]}}</ref> The manga was nominated for the 11th edition of the [[Manga Taishō]] awards in 2018 and it managed to gain a total of 47 points.<ref>https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-03-22/paru-itagaki-beastars-wins-11th-manga-taisho-awards/.129344</ref>

